/* Details *******************************************
 * I2C communication
 *  BME280 : Barometric Pressure, humidity, temperature
 *  MLX90614 : Temperature(Infrared temperature sensor)
 *  MPU9250 : Acceleration, Gyro
 *  no 9D-compass(bno055)
 * Serial communication
 *  GPS : Time, Longitude, Latitude
******************************************************/

